 The DPU-SCUI shall cancel the write to each subaddress if the SCU fails to read a pending STPDU after a timeout specified by a value calculated based on the SCU_POLL_RATE parameter provided during initialization, shall record new data to those subaddresses, and report an error to the DPU-CCM.  The SCU_POLL RATE parameter shall have a default setting of J ms and shall be capable of being modified dynamically.
